@startuml
hide footbox
actor 管理员
participant "前端页面" as Frontend
participant "BaseMatController" as Controller
participant "BaseMatServiceImpl" as Service
database "MySQL数据库" as DB

管理员 -> Frontend: 点击新增，填写物料信息
Frontend -> Frontend: 表单验证

Frontend -> Controller: POST /base/mat
Controller -> Controller: 权限校验，设置创建人

Controller -> Service: insertBaseMat(baseMat)
Service -> Service: 设置创建时间

Service -> DB: INSERT INTO base_mat
DB --> Service: 返回影响行数

Service --> Controller: 返回结果
Controller --> Frontend: 返回AjaxResult响应

Frontend --> 管理员: 关闭对话框，刷新列表

@enduml